# radroots-events-codec

Reference encoders and decoders for Rad Roots Nostr event payloads.

## Goals

- define stable encoding and decoding interfaces for Rad Roots event payloads
- keep parsing and validation behavior deterministic across supported event forms
- support std and no_std builds with feature-gated `serde_json` and Nostr integration
- provide reusable codec primitives for higher-level Rad Roots crates

